What is Third Party Payments  ?

The payment that has been made to any other Person(Not you), such as your Buyer or your Friend, then that payment is called third party payment. In this, your Father, Mother, Brother, Sister account will also count in Third Party Payment.

Buyer :  Because you will get the payment done by the buyer to us and will take crypto from us and the buyer will be successful.
Friend : Nowadays no friend gives even a single rupee, your friend cannot give it to you to buy crypto.
Mother / Father : You will secretly buy crypto from your father's or mother's account and delete the message, but later they will come to know, they will ask the bank, not you, and the bank will dispute the payment.
Brother / Sister : These two are such people that you will die but still will not give money, so this one should not lie that brother has paid because brother will never give you money to buy crypto.

